      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REMEMBRANCE TIME (6) was a beaten favourite last time but still gave a sight, leading and sticking on for second at this circuit. May enjoy the longer trip having won easily over 2100m on debut three back at Geelong. She has more upside than most of these. FLING IT RAINBOW (1) added to a string of top-three results when she came from this barrier to be beaten less than 3m at Cranbourne last start. Good effort to score at Geelong prior. Major player. SILENT REVERIE (7) draws wide but is building in fitness and looks close to a win after three nice efforts off a spell, leading for second at Geelong last week. ALLWATFUNJINGLES (4) bombed the start last time but was good in a Melton placing prior. IMABOGANBOY (3) draws well and has some claims off a placing here two back.",
